Nicholas Pence, 25, and his father David were shot dead 'execution-style' at their home in New Orleans on Wednesday . 
  They had been celebrating a football game in their garage when they were killed . 
  David Pence was shot three times in the chest while his son was shot in the face and back . 
  Dexter Allen, 17, and Haraqyon Degruy, 18, have been charged with the double killing . 
  Police believe it was a botched burglary after guests left the house . 
 